_foo.php</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"changed-files\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#changed-files\" aria-label=\"changed files permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Changed files</h3>\n<p>There are no changed files.</p>\n<h2 id=\"test-your-joomla-module\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#test-your-joomla-module\" aria-label=\"test your joomla module permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Test your Joomla module</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>install your module in Joomla version 4 to test it. In the beginning, the easiest thing to do is to copy the files manually in place:</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Copy the files in the <code class=\"language-text\">modules</code> folder to the <code class=\"language-text\">modules</code> folder of your Joomla 4 installation.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>install your module as described in part one, after you have copied all files. Open the menu <code class=\"language-text\">System | Install | Discover</code>. Here you will see an entry for the module you just copied. Select it and click on the button <code class=\"language-text\">Install</code>. 3.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Next, test if your module works properly. Open the menu 'Content | Site Modules' and click in the toolbar <code class=\"language-text\">New</code>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/191e2/j4x36x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Test Joomla Module\"\n        title=\"Test Joomla Module\"\n        src=\"/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/5a190/j4x36x1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/772e8/j4x36x1.png 200w,\n/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/e17e5/j4x36x1.png 400w,\n/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/5a190/j4x36x1.png 800w,\n/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/c1b63/j4x36x1.png 1200w,\n/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/29007/j4x36x1.png 1600w,\n/static/c3d7b8bf52b41db8087618587a00ce9c/191e2/j4x36x1.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9482dbbdb14794110ac4d96d6eae9b9e/19